WEBVTT

00:07.500 --> 00:08.866
Collect your pay, ya done.

00:08.867 --> 00:09.667
(Leonard yelling)

00:09.668 --> 00:10.832
Chester just lay off.

00:10.833 --> 00:12.832
Save the smart mouth
for ya boyfriend.

00:12.833 --> 00:14.332
<i>Leonard: Here
comes trouble.</i>

00:14.333 --> 00:15.366
So you want something?

00:15.367 --> 00:17.632
How would you like to make
200,000 dollars?

00:17.633 --> 00:19.032
Hap: I got a deal.

00:19.033 --> 00:20.367
A lot o' money.

00:20.567 --> 00:21.567
We gotta shoot somebody?

00:21.633 --> 00:22.633
<i>Trudy: This is chub.</i>

00:22.800 --> 00:24.066
I'm Paco.

00:24.067 --> 00:25.000
There's a million dollars

00:25.001 --> 00:26.168
at the bottom of that river.

00:26.533 --> 00:28.099
What the hell you smilin' about?!

00:28.100 --> 00:30.267
Soldier: Ooooooh!

00:31.767 --> 00:35.100
I'm lookin' for a man named Paco.

00:36.200 --> 00:40.332
[footsteps rustling]

00:40.333 --> 00:43.166
<i>[solemn music]</i>

00:43.167 --> 00:45.066
This is the spot.

00:45.067 --> 00:47.832
My daddy says they hung him
down there by the river.

00:47.833 --> 00:49.599
Skinned that old nigga,
but he was still alive

00:49.600 --> 00:51.832
when they hanged him.

00:51.833 --> 00:54.466
Ain't no such thing as ghosts.

00:54.467 --> 00:56.699
They say he hung there
all night.

00:56.700 --> 00:59.200
Cryin' till he died.

01:01.867 --> 01:04.066
Look.

01:04.066 --> 01:06.266
Shit, just an old rope.

01:06.267 --> 01:08.199
Folks say you come
down here at night,

01:08.200 --> 01:10.799
you could still hear him cryin'.

01:10.800 --> 01:13.800
<i>[distant howling]</i>

01:17.633 --> 01:19.866
<i>[howling]</i>

01:19.867 --> 01:20.899
[crow caws]

01:20.900 --> 01:23.166
[both yelling]

01:23.167 --> 01:26.166
[crow cawing]

01:26.167 --> 01:30.366
<i>[dramatic music]</i>

01:30.367 --> 01:32.532
Damn.
I almost shit myself.

01:32.533 --> 01:34.766
[chuckles]
I did.

01:34.767 --> 01:38.999
[both screaming]

01:39.000 --> 01:42.332
<i>♪ ♪</i>

01:42.333 --> 01:45.299
<i>[dramatic percussive music]</i>

01:45.300 --> 01:53.300
<i>♪ ♪</i>

01:55.000 --> 02:01.074
